name: Dark Collaboration (V)
Lore: 'Imperial leaders are ruthlessly effective when working together. Tarkin, Motti and Tagge presented a deadly combination as they plotted to ''crush the Rebellion.''',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to take into hand an Imperial Council Member (or Bewil) or deploy a site with ''ISB'' in title or game text from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR During battle, your total power is +X, where X = your total influence at Conference Room (limit +6).',
